snippet.title: Super Zoo Story (Stardew Valley-Like) - Official Gameplay Trailer | Summer of Gaming 2022
snippet.description:
Be a manager and zookeeper of the zoo of your dreams in Super Zoo Story, an open-world simulator with RPG elements in a pixel art style. This upcoming indie game is inspired by Stardew Valley and can be wishlisted on Steam now.
